<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dashboard – Tinchost Panel</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #f5f5f5; }
    .nav { background: #222; color: #fff; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 1rem; }
    main { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.5rem; background: #fff; min-height: 80vh; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
    .card h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="/">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/sites">Sites</a>
    <a href="/databases">Databases</a>
    <a href="/mail">Mail</a>
    <a href="/settings">Settings</a>
    <span style="float:right"><%= user.username %> | <a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a></span>
  </nav>
  <main>
    <h1>Hello, <%= user.username %></h1>
    <p>Tinchost Panel. Manage sites, databases, and mail from the menu.</p>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Quick links</h2>
      <p><a href="/sites">Sites</a> – Add or edit websites (Nginx, PHP version, SSL, FTP).</p>
      <p><a href="/databases">Databases</a> – Create MySQL/MariaDB databases and users.</p>
      <p><a href="/mail">Mail</a> – Mail domains and mailboxes.</p>
      <p><a href="/settings">Settings</a> – Paths and wizard state.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
